    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/redapm25/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u13208503-80.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/redapm25/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蜷川新右衛門</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-03-10"
      class="main-meta">2014-03-10 15:47:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6581058_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  没有看过译本，而是看的原著。虽然对于京都学派大师们的巨著来说，这本书略显单薄，但是对于隋唐史研究感兴趣的人来说，算得上一本相当不错入门书籍。建议补充阅读与之相关的京都学派的隋唐论著。      

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
